{"data":[{"date":"02:10 01/07","title":"Pogba: \"Mbappe t\u00e0i n\u0103ng h\u01a1n t\u00f4i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/pogba-mbappe-tai-nang-hon-toi.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kylian Mbappe, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho M.U kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh thua k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Kylian Mbappe b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Argentina \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018, ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Kylian Mbappe \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. Ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1998 g\u00f3p d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 3 trong 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Les Bleus.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kylian Mbappe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kylian Mbappe h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/pogba-mbappe-tai-nang-hon-toi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Kylian Mbappe l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap tr\u01b0\u1edbc Argentina</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Mbappe gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p mang v\u1ec1 1 qu\u1ea3 11m sau \u0111\u00f3 Antoine Griezmann th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng, sau \u0111\u00f3 t\u1eeb ph\u00fat 64 \u0111\u1ebfn ph\u00fat 68 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG l\u1eadp m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb sau Pele v\u00e0o n\u0103m 1958 m\u1edbi l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u01b0\u1edbi 20 tu\u1ed5i l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n ng\u00f4i sao 19 tu\u1ed5i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a Mbappe l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p h\u1ea1 Argentina 4-3 \u0111\u1ec3 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. T\u00ednh ra c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1998 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Pogba khen ng\u1ee3i Mbappe</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Paul Pogba ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Kylian Mbappe, ng\u00f4i sao \u0111ang thi \u0111\u1ea5u cho M.U kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh thua k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed3ng h\u01b0\u01a1ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi Ph\u00e1p v\u1ec1 m\u1eb7t t\u00e0i n\u0103ng.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"2 cau thu Argentina tranh chap voi Pogba\" title=\"2 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Argentina tranh ch\u1ea5p v\u1edbi Pogba\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/pogba-6.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Pogba t\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Mbappe</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201c\u1ede tu\u1ed5i 19, t\u00f4i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nhi\u1ec1u. Ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn nh\u1eefng g\u00ec t\u00f4i th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n thua k\u00e9m c\u1eadu \u1ea5y r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u, t\u00f4i t\u1ef1 nh\u1eadn m\u00ecnh kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 so s\u00e1nh v\u1edbi Mbappe. C\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng t\u1ed1 ch\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t ng\u00f4i sao h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cMbappe c\u00f3 kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ed1t, c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f3 k\u1ef9 thu\u1eadt v\u00e0 t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u00e1ng n\u1ec3, t\u00f4i tin c\u1eadu \u1ea5y c\u00f2n ph\u00e1t tri\u1ec3n n\u1eefa trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Hy v\u1ecdng c\u1eadu \u1ea5y s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c duy tr\u00ec phong \u0111\u1ed9 t\u1ed1t \u1edf nh\u1eefng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ti\u1ebfp theo, qua \u0111\u00f3 gi\u00fap Ph\u00e1p ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-phap-43-argentina-421-190036.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-phap-43-argentina.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-phap-43-argentina-421-190036.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-3 Argentina</span><br>\r\nPh\u00e1p v\u00e0 Argentina \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u m\u00e3n nh\u00e3n v\u1edbi 7 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi, Les Bleus l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i ngh\u1eb9t th\u1edf 4-3. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y, Ph\u00e1p \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n v\u00e0 x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng. V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n Argentina x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 t\u00f4n tr\u1ecdng\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"757","checkdouble":"190040"},{"date":"02:44 01/07","title":"Thua Ph\u00e1p b\u1ebd b\u00e0ng, hai tr\u1ee5 c\u1ed9t c\u00f9ng n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0110T Argentina","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/thua-phap-be-bang-javier-mascherano-chia-tay-dt-argentina.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018, Javier Mascherano v\u00e0 Lucas Biglia c\u00f9ng n\u00f3i l\u1eddi gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf trong n\u1ed7i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-argentina-461-190009.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/Antoine-Griezmann-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Phap-vs-Argentina-hinh-anh.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-phap-vs-argentina-461-190009.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Ph\u00e1p 4-3 Argentina (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u00e0i th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m g\u1eb7p kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n b\u1ecb d\u1eabn tr\u01b0\u1edbc song nh\u1edd v\u00e0o s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a sao tr\u1ebb Mbappe, Les Bleus \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng l\u1ee3i chung cu\u1ed9c s\u00e1t n\u00fat \u0111\u1ec3 ghi danh...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Javier Mascherano chia tay \u0110T Argentina</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong s\u1ed1 23 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 d\u1ef1 World Cup 2018 c\u1ee7a \u0110T Argentina, Javier Mascherano l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean nhi\u1ec1u tu\u1ed5i nh\u1ea5t (34). V\u00ec v\u1eady, nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 Mascherano s\u1ebd n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay sau gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh s\u1ef1 th\u1eadt khi c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1984 \u0111\u00e3 n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0110T Argentina.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thua Ph\u00e1p b\u1ebd b\u00e0ng, Javier Mascherano chia tay \u0110T Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Thua Ph\u00e1p b\u1ebd b\u00e0ng, Javier Mascherano chia tay \u0110T Argentina h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/thua-phap-be-bang-javier-mascherano-chia-tay-dt-argentina.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Javier Mascherano chia tay \u0110T Argentina sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&quot;Gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i chia tay, gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n t\u1eeb ngo\u00e0i s\u00e2n. Hy v\u1ecdng trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai, nh\u1eefng ch\u00e0ng trai n\u00e0y c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec \u0111\u00f3&quot; - Javier Mascherano chia s\u1ebb ngay sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i c\u1ee7a \u0110T Argentina t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 16 \u0111\u1ed9i, Mascherano c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Albiceleste cho th\u1ea5y v\u1ebft h\u1eb1n c\u1ee7a tu\u1ed5i t\u00e1c. H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Argentina kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 \u0111ua t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb trung h\u01a1n b\u00ean ph\u00eda \u0110T Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 Kylian Mbappe d\u1eabn t\u1edbi 4 b\u00e0n thua.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mascherano \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 147 tr\u1eadn cho \u0110T Argentina, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/jorge-sampaoli-khong-tu-chuc-du-dt-argentina-bi-loai-465-190037.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/jorge-sampaoli-khong-tu-chuc-du-dt-argentina-bi-loai.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/jorge-sampaoli-khong-tu-chuc-du-dt-argentina-bi-loai-465-190037.html\">Jorge Sampaoli kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c d\u00f9 \u0110T Argentina b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i</span><br>\r\nD\u00f9 \u0110T Argentina \u0111\u00e3 r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 sau tr\u1eadn thua Ph\u00e1p nh\u01b0ng HLV Jorge Sampaoli kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c sau nh\u1eefng \u00e1p l\u1ef1c k\u00e9o d\u00e0i su\u1ed1t t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u gi\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Biglia c\u0169ng n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Mascherano l\u00e0 c\u00e1i t\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean n\u00f3i l\u1eddi chia tay \u0110T Argentina v\u00e0 k\u00e9o theo hi\u1ec7u \u1ee9ng domino. Kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u sau \u0111\u00f3, ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Lucas Biglia c\u0169ng tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gi\u00e3 t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p thi \u0111\u1ea5u qu\u1ed1c t\u1ebf sau khi \u0110T Argentina b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lucas Biglia cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i v\u1edbi n\u1ed7i bu\u1ed3n b\u1edfi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 \u0111o\u1ea1n cu\u1ed1i con \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 th\u00e0nh vi\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i. Hy v\u1ecdng nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u1ebd l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c v\u1edbi \u00e1p l\u1ef1c nh\u1ecf h\u01a1n, gi\u00fap Argentina \u0111\u1ea1t \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1ecb tr\u00ed x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00f4i b\u01b0\u1edbc sang m\u1ed9t b\u00ean. Th\u00e0nh th\u1eadt m\u00e0 n\u00f3i, Argentina \u0111ang c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf h\u1ec7 m\u1edbi gi\u00e0u t\u00e0i n\u0103ng v\u00e0 gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ecd ti\u1ebfp qu\u1ea3n&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lucas Biglia n\u0103m nay 32 tu\u1ed5i v\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 58 tr\u1eadn ra s\u00e2n cho \u0110T Argentina, ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<h2><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Argentina t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/griezmann-phap-xung-dang-gianh-ve-vao-tu-ket-421-190038.html\">Griezmann: Ph\u00e1p x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/jorge-sampaoli-khong-tu-chuc-du-dt-argentina-bi-loai-465-190037.html\">Jorge Sampaoli kh\u00f4ng t\u1eeb ch\u1ee9c d\u00f9 \u0110T Argentina b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/4-nguoi-chien-thang-va-3-nguoi-that-bai-sau-tran-phap-43-argentina-421-190036.html\">4 ng\u01b0\u1eddi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u00e0 3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i sau tr\u1eadn Ph\u00e1p 4-3 Argentina</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-didier-deschamps-tin-vao-suc-manh-dt-phap-465-190035.html\">H\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Argentina, HLV Didier Deschamps t\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh \u0110T Ph\u00e1p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/kylian-mbappe-hanh-dien-khi-duoc-so-voi-pele-465-190032.html\">San b\u1eb1ng th\u00e0nh t\u00edch c\u1ee7a vua b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Pele, Kylian Mbappe n\u00f3i g\u00ec?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nhung-thong-ke-dang-nho-sau-tran-dau-phap-43-argentina-421-190030.html\">Nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Ph\u00e1p 4-3 Argentina</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"756","checkdouble":"190042"},{"date":"03:11 01/07","title":"Messi l\u1ea7m l\u0169i th\u00e1o b\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng sau khi Argentina thua Ph\u00e1p","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/11.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Uruguay, song r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. CR7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u1ea1c l\u00f5ng gi\u1eefa v\u00f2ng v\u00e2y c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Uruguay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/5-diem-nhan-Uruguay-vs-Bo-Dao-Nha-vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Ronaldo ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 24 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 c\u1ee7a Uruguay. CR7 b\u1ecb chia c\u1eaft ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1edbi 6 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n k\u1ebft th\u00fac c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao b\u00ean ph\u00eda Uruguay (5) song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup, ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t&nbsp;trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-2 qua \u0111\u00f3 d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Edison Cavani</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Ronaldo b\u00ean ph\u00eda B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i th\u00ec Edison Cavani c\u1ee7a Uruguay l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. Ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 7, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cavani nang ty so len 2-1\" title=\"Cavani n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/cavabi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cavani t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Suarez, Cavani di chuy\u1ec3n th\u00f4ng minh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Rui Patricio \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 44 c\u1ee7a Cavani cho Uruguay, trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y 12 do Luis Suarez ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n27% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 Cavani c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c do Luis Suarez ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y hi\u1ec3u nhau nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1966, ch\u1ec9 Grzegorz Lato v\u00e0 Andrzej Szarmach (5, Ba Lan) v\u00e0 Michael Ballack v\u00e0 Miroslav Klose (5, \u0110\u1ee9c) l\u00e0 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n&nbsp;th\u1eafng h\u01a1n Edinson Cavani v\u00e0 Luis Suarez (4, Uruguay).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 62, t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Rodrigo Bentancur, Cavani t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Patricio l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2. Pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018, Cavani x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n so v\u1edbi Uruguay, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 67% v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m g\u1ea5p 4 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 (20 so v\u1edbi 5), th\u1eadm ch\u00ed m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Ronaldo (6) c\u00f2n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n h\u00e3m th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Uruguay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tinh huong Pepe go hoa 1-1\" title=\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Pepe g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/022738-pepe.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn thua tr\u1eadn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSeleccao c\u0169ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Uruguay v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c (10 so v\u1edbi 2) v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n, song s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng&nbsp; c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00ec h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i thua k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf khi\u1ebfn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-bo-dao-nha-vs-uruguay-421-190013.html\" target=\"_blank\">k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span> gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina 4-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pepe v\u00e0 Fonte l\u00e0 t\u1eed huy\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pepe v\u00e0 Fonte, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Fernando Santos s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i l\u00ean t\u1edbi 69, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c b\u00ean kia c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng nh\u1edd y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fonte va Pepe khong hoan thanh nhiem vu\" title=\"Fonte v\u00e0 Pepe kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/040406-fonte.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fonte v\u00e0 Pepe kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nUruguay \u0111\u00e3 khai th\u00e1c c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf trung l\u1ed9, c\u1ea3 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p c\u1ee7a hai trung v\u1ec7 b\u00ean ph\u00eda B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Cavani, Pepe v\u00e0 Fonte kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 nhanh \u0111\u1ec3 quan s\u00e1t vi\u1ec7c Cavani l\u1ebbn xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng treo b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Suarez. \u1ede c\u1ef1 ly r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ai k\u00e8m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 31 tu\u1ed5i, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Cavani th\u00ec b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m g\u1ecdn trong l\u01b0\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFonte v\u00e0 Pepe kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 nhanh nh\u1eb9n v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 phong t\u1ecfa nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00ean ph\u00eda Uruguay, ch\u00ednh s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn B\u0110N nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Uruguay x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Edison Cavani \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng khi \u0111em v\u1ec1 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 b\u00ean ph\u00eda Uruguay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hang thu Uruguay da phong toa rat tot Ronaldo\" title=\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 phong t\u1ecfa r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/hang-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 phong t\u1ecfa r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Pepe sau m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m th\u00ec c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd khi\u1ebfn Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh c\u00f2n Adrien Silva b\u1ecb thay ra t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGodin ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Gimenez, Laxalt v\u00e0 Caceres c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018, Uruguay ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n thua.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nUruguay \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018, ch\u00ednh s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Uruguay 2-1 Bo Dao Nha\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Thong-so-BDN.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"755","checkdouble":"190043"},{"date":"04:21 01/07","title":"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua tr\u1eadn Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/5-diem-nhan-Uruguay-vs-Bo-Dao-Nha-vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay qua \u0111\u00f3 nh\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>0 \u2013 </strong>Cristiano Ronaldo v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 6 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, tung ra 25 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, v\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, v\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/5-diem-nhan-Uruguay-vs-Bo-Dao-Nha-vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo ch\u01b0a ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</p>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>6 - </strong>Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 6 l\u1ea7n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Uruguay, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 (5) trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>5 \u2013 </strong>Trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Uruguay ch\u1ec9 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u00f3 5 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng mang v\u1ec1 t\u1edbi 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>597 - </strong>B\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Pepe cho B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ea5m d\u1ee9t chu\u1ed7i 597 ph\u00fat gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi c\u1ee7a Uruguay, tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u1ea7n g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t m\u00e0 h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec3 th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u1ebfn\u00a0v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m 2017 trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u00c1o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>0 \u2013 </strong>Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 24 ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng trong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo khong cham bong mot lan nao trong vong cam Uruguay trong hiep 1\" title=\"Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Uruguay trong hi\u1ec7p 1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/ronaldo-7.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m Uruguay trong hi\u1ec7p 1</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<strong>4 - </strong>K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1966, ch\u1ec9 Grzegorz Lato v\u00e0 Andrzej Szarmach (5, Ba Lan), Michael Ballack v\u00e0 Miroslav Klose (5, \u0110\u1ee9c) \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Edinson Cavani v\u00e0 Luis Suarez (4, Uruguay).\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br>\r\n12 -</strong> Luis Suarez \u0111\u00e3 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o 12/44 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Edison Cavani trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG (chi\u1ebfm 27%).</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"754","checkdouble":"190046"},{"date":"04:37 01/07","title":"Thua Uruguay, HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha xin Ronaldo m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/santos.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Fernando Santos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 63 tu\u1ed5i hy v\u1ecdng Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho Seleccao thay v\u00ec chia tay \u0110TQG.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Fernando Santos hy v\u1ecdng Cristiano Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng chia tay \u0110TQG</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay, anh d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1edbi 6 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. \u0110\u1ebfn th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m hi\u1ec7n t\u1ea1i CR7 \u0111\u00e3 ra s\u00e2n 6 l\u1ea7n \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 25 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fernando Santos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Fernando Santos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Fernando-Santos-phat-bieu-ve-tran-Uruguay-vs-Bo-Dao-Nha-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Santos hy v\u1ecdng Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng chia tay \u0110TQG</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha thua 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay qua \u0111\u00f3 d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup. Th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, CR7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 chia tay \u0110TQG.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFernando Santos ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, \u00f4ng th\u1ea7y 63 tu\u1ed5i hy v\u1ecdng Cristiano Ronaldo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho Seleccao thay v\u00ec chia tay \u0110TQG.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo v\u1eabn r\u1ea5t quan tr\u1ecdng v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 9 v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Ronaldo s\u1ebd ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c s\u00e1t c\u00e1nh c\u00f9ng \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n c\u1eadu \u1ea5y chia tay \u0110TQG\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201c\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang g\u1eb7p m\u1ed9t s\u1ed1 kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111ang \u1edf giai \u0111o\u1ea1n chuy\u1ec3n giao. R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u1edbn tu\u1ed5i s\u1ebd \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c thay th\u1ebf b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 tr\u1ebb, t\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng Ronaldo s\u1ebd \u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ee1 nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 thi\u1ebfu kinh nghi\u1ec7m\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Fernando Santos t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c sau tr\u1eadn thua Uruguay</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-bo-dao-nha-vs-uruguay-421-190013.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span> khi\u1ebfn Seleccao nh\u01b0\u1eddng v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft cho \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7, n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9, HLV Fernando Santos kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Santos noi ve tran Uruguay vs Bo Dao Nha\" title=\"HLV Santos n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/santos.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Santos n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ebft s\u1ee9c. B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 ghi nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecf l\u1ee1 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i. Uruguay l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng m\u1ea1nh, h\u1ecd x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-uruguay-21-bo-dao-nha-421-190048.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-uruguay-21-bo-dao-nha.JPG\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-uruguay-21-bo-dao-nha-421-190048.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span><br>\r\nUruguay \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n\u201cH\u00f4m nay l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y bu\u1ed3n v\u1edbi NHM b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec1n \u0111\u00e1p ni\u1ec1m tin t\u1eeb h\u1ecd. Thay m\u1eb7t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng t\u00f4i g\u1eedi l\u1eddi xin l\u1ed7i \u0111\u1ebfn NHM, ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd \u1edf nh\u1eefng gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1edbi\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nL\u00ea H\u01b0\u1eddng (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"753","checkdouble":"190047"},{"date":"04:08 01/07","title":"5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-uruguay-21-bo-dao-nha.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha 2-1 \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018, c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1ea5t.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCristiano Ronaldo l\u00e0 ng\u00f4i sao \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Uruguay, song r\u1ea5t ti\u1ebfc c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 sinh n\u0103m 1985 \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng. CR7 ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n l\u1ea1c l\u00f5ng gi\u1eefa v\u00f2ng v\u00e2y c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Uruguay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"5 \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/5-diem-nhan-Uruguay-vs-Bo-Dao-Nha-vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong 45 ph\u00fat \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Ronaldo ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng 24 l\u1ea7n nh\u01b0ng t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u b\u00ean ngo\u00e0i khu v\u1ef1c 16m50 c\u1ee7a Uruguay. CR7 b\u1ecb chia c\u1eaft ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh, nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 c\u1ee7a anh c\u0169ng kh\u00f4ng \u0111em l\u1ea1i k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 nh\u01b0 mong \u0111\u1ee3i.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nM\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n t\u1edbi 6 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n k\u1ebft th\u00fac c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c ng\u00f4i sao b\u00ean ph\u00eda Uruguay (5) song kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp \u1edf m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup, ch\u00ednh m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a Ronaldo l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t&nbsp;trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ec3 thua 1-2 qua \u0111\u00f3 d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u00f9ng Edison Cavani</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">N\u1ebfu nh\u01b0 Ronaldo b\u00ean ph\u00eda B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ec7 h\u1ea1i th\u00ec Edison Cavani c\u1ee7a Uruguay l\u1ea1i c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f9ng n\u1ed5. Ngay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 7, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG \u0111\u00e3 m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cavani nang ty so len 2-1\" title=\"Cavani n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/cavabi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cavani t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Suarez, Cavani di chuy\u1ec3n th\u00f4ng minh tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Rui Patricio \u1edf c\u1ef1 ly g\u1ea7n. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 44 c\u1ee7a Cavani cho Uruguay, trong s\u1ed1 n\u00e0y 12 do Luis Suarez ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n27% s\u1ed1 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 Cavani c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c do Luis Suarez ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o, \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y hi\u1ec3u nhau nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1966, ch\u1ec9 Grzegorz Lato v\u00e0 Andrzej Szarmach (5, Ba Lan) v\u00e0 Michael Ballack v\u00e0 Miroslav Klose (5, \u0110\u1ee9c) l\u00e0 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n&nbsp;th\u1eafng h\u01a1n Edinson Cavani v\u00e0 Luis Suarez (4, Uruguay).&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCh\u01b0a d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i \u1edf \u0111\u00f3, t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 62, t\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng nh\u1ea3 b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Rodrigo Bentancur, Cavani t\u1ea1o n\u00ean m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng cong tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1eb9p \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Patricio l\u1ea7n th\u1ee9 2. Pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng n\u00e0y gi\u00fap Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u1edbi c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c, tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018, Cavani x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 l\u00e0 v\u00f4 ngh\u0129a</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u00e3 \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n so v\u1edbi Uruguay, h\u1ecd c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ebfn 67% v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m g\u1ea5p 4 l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 (20 so v\u1edbi 5), th\u1eadm ch\u00ed m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh Ronaldo (6) c\u00f2n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n h\u00e3m th\u00e0nh c\u1ee7a Uruguay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Tinh huong Pepe go hoa 1-1\" title=\"T\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng Pepe g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 1-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/022738-pepe.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u00e1p \u0111\u1ea3o v\u1ec1 m\u1ecdi ch\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn thua tr\u1eadn</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nSeleccao c\u0169ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i so v\u1edbi Uruguay v\u1ec1 s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n ph\u1ea1t g\u00f3c (10 so v\u1edbi 2) v\u00e0 s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng chuy\u1ec1n, song s\u1ed1 l\u01b0\u1ee3ng b\u00e0n th\u1eafng&nbsp; c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00ec h\u1ecd l\u1ea1i thua k\u00e9m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nKh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ea1n ch\u1ebf khi\u1ebfn B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1ea5t th\u1ee7 1-2 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay, <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-bo-dao-nha-vs-uruguay-421-190013.html\" target=\"_blank\">k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span> gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a Nam M\u1ef9 b\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Ph\u00e1p, \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Argentina 4-3 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Pepe v\u00e0 Fonte l\u00e0 t\u1eed huy\u1ec7t c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Pepe v\u00e0 Fonte, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c HLV Fernando Santos s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay c\u00f3 s\u1ed1 tu\u1ed5i c\u1ed9ng l\u1ea1i l\u00ean t\u1edbi 69, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 b\u01b0\u1edbc sang s\u01b0\u1eddn d\u1ed1c b\u00ean kia c\u1ee7a s\u1ef1 nghi\u1ec7p v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 c\u00f2n ch\u01a1i b\u00f3ng nh\u1edd y\u1ebfu t\u1ed1 kinh nghi\u1ec7m.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Fonte va Pepe khong hoan thanh nhiem vu\" title=\"Fonte v\u00e0 Pepe kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/040406-fonte.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Fonte v\u00e0 Pepe kh\u00f4ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nUruguay \u0111\u00e3 khai th\u00e1c c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t v\u00e0o v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf trung l\u1ed9, c\u1ea3 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb s\u1ef1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p c\u1ee7a hai trung v\u1ec7 b\u00ean ph\u00eda B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u1ede b\u00e0n th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean c\u1ee7a Cavani, Pepe v\u00e0 Fonte kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 nhanh \u0111\u1ec3 quan s\u00e1t vi\u1ec7c Cavani l\u1ebbn xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u00f3n \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng treo b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a Suarez. \u1ede c\u1ef1 ly r\u1ea5t g\u1ea7n v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ai k\u00e8m c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u0110\u1ebfn pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9 2 c\u1ee7a ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o 31 tu\u1ed5i, b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha th\u1eadm ch\u00ed ch\u01b0a k\u1ecbp \u0111\u1ecbnh h\u00ecnh c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a Cavani th\u00ec b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eb1m g\u1ecdn trong l\u01b0\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nFonte v\u00e0 Pepe kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 nhanh nh\u1eb9n v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ec3 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 phong t\u1ecfa nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng b\u00ean ph\u00eda Uruguay, ch\u00ednh s\u1ef1 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn B\u0110N nh\u1eadn th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 1-2.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Uruguay x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c nh\u1eefng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Luis Suarez v\u00e0 Edison Cavani \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng khi \u0111em v\u1ec1 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng ph\u1ea3i k\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ebfn phong \u0111\u1ed9 \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 l\u00e0m nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 b\u00ean ph\u00eda Uruguay.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Hang thu Uruguay da phong toa rat tot Ronaldo\" title=\"H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 phong t\u1ecfa r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t Ronaldo\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/hang-thu.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 phong t\u1ecfa r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgo\u1ea1i tr\u1eeb t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng d\u1eabn \u0111\u1ebfn b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Pepe sau m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng h\u1ed7n lo\u1ea1n trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m th\u00ec c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Uruguay \u0111\u00e3 ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, h\u1ecd khi\u1ebfn Ronaldo kh\u00f4ng c\u00f2n l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh c\u00f2n Adrien Silva b\u1ecb thay ra t\u1eeb r\u1ea5t s\u1edbm.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nGodin ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c cho th\u1ea5y kinh nghi\u1ec7m v\u00e0 b\u00f3ng d\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t th\u1ee7 l\u0129nh, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Gimenez, Laxalt v\u00e0 Caceres c\u0169ng ho\u00e0n th\u00e0nh xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nhi\u1ec7m v\u1ee5 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. 4 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018, Uruguay ch\u1ec9 nh\u1eadn duy nh\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n thua.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nUruguay \u0111ang l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t World Cup 2018, ch\u00ednh s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn n\u01a1i h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 \u0111ang l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec3m t\u1ef1a gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 ti\u1ebfn s\u00e2u \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u00ean \u0111\u1ea5t Nga.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha<span style=\"white-space:pre\">\t</span><br>\r\n</strong><br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Thong so tran dau Uruguay 2-1 Bo Dao Nha\" title=\"Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Thong-so-BDN.png\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Th\u00f4ng s\u1ed1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"752","checkdouble":"190048"},{"date":"06:43 01/07","title":"HLV Uruguay ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cavani","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/hlv-uruguay-tiet-lo-tinh-hinh-chan-thuong-cua-cavani.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Oscar Tabarez ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a ch\u00e2n s\u00fat Edinson Cavani sau khi Uruguay \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bo-dao-nha-vs-uruguay-461-190020.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/cavabi.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-bo-dao-nha-vs-uruguay-461-190020.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (V\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nTrong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y Ronaldo im ti\u1ebfng, nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch ch\u00e2u \u00c2u \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i tr\u01b0\u1edbc m\u1ed9t Uruguay v\u1ed1n d\u0129 qu\u00e1 tinh qu\u00e1i v\u00e0 b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh. C\u1ea3 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n Nam M\u1ef9 \u0111\u1ec1u...</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cavani ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 ch\u00e2u \u00c2u, Uruguay gi\u00e0nh t\u1ea5m v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-1 nh\u1edd s\u1ef1 t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng c\u1ee7a Cavani. Ch\u00e2n s\u00fat 31 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 l\u1eadp c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap nh\u01b0ng ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi s\u00e2n v\u1edbi v\u1ebb \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn. \u0110\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd l\u00e0 ch\u00ednh Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 v\u1ecbn \u0111\u1ec3 Cavani r\u1eddi s\u00e2n.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Uruguay tiet lo tinh hinh chan thuong cua Cavani.\" title=\"HLV Uruguay ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cavani.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/hlv-uruguay-tiet-lo-tinh-hinh-chan-thuong-cua-cavani.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Uruguay ti\u1ebft l\u1ed9 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cavani.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTi\u1ebft l\u1ed9 v\u1ec1 t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cavani sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, HLV Oscar Tabarez cho bi\u1ebft: &quot;Anh \u1ea5y d\u00ednh ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ee3i. M\u1ee9c \u0111\u1ed9 ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u1ee7a Cavani ch\u01b0a \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c x\u00e1c \u0111\u1ecbnh&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">E ng\u1ea1i \u0110T Ph\u00e1p<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Uruguay s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Ph\u00e1p trong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. V\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c Cavani ch\u1ea5n th\u01b0\u01a1ng c\u00f3 nguy c\u01a1 v\u1eafng m\u1eb7t, \u0110T Uruguay g\u1eb7p th\u00eam kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n khi ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Les Bleus, \u0111\u1ed9i v\u1eeba h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c Argentina v\u1edbi vi\u1ec7c ghi \u0111\u1ebfn 4 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Oscar Tabarez e ng\u1ea1i: &quot;S\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb t\u1eadp th\u1ec3. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 n\u1ec1n t\u1ea3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ed1ng l\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o, v\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u0169ng nh\u1eadn th\u1ee9c \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Ph\u00e1p l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i. H\u1ecd c\u00f3 hai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o phi th\u01b0\u1eddng l\u00e0 Griezmann v\u00e0 Mbappe, c\u1ea3 hai \u0111\u1ec1u r\u1ea5t nhanh&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;C\u00e1c b\u1ea1n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y c\u00e1c h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 ph\u1ea3i v\u1eadt l\u1ed9n khi \u0111\u01b0\u01a1ng \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Mbappe trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Argentina. \u0110\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 th\u1eed th\u00e1ch kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n cho ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. Nh\u01b0ng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng l\u00e0m nh\u1eefng \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u1ed1t nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i theo c\u00e1ch c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh, t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a ch\u00fang t\u00f4i&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&quot;Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ea3 b\u1ea3y tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ti\u1ebfn t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft v\u00e0 h\u00e3y xem \u0111i\u1ec1u g\u00ec s\u1ebd x\u1ea3y ra&quot;.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Uruguay vs Ph\u00e1p s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 21h00 ng\u00e0y 6/7.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Uruguay t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/du-am-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-thanh-bai-boi-nhung-hong-sung-421-190052.html\">D\u01b0 \u00e2m Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: Th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdng s\u00fang</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/5-dieu-rut-ra-sau-tran-uruguay-21-bo-dao-nha-421-190048.html\">5 \u0111i\u1ec1u r\u00fat ra sau tr\u1eadn Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thua-uruguay-hlv-bo-dao-nha-xin-ronaldo-mot-dieu-421-190047.html\">Thua Uruguay, HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha xin Ronaldo m\u1ed9t \u0111i\u1ec1u</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-uruguay-21-bo-dao-nha-421-190046.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 b\u1ecf qua tr\u1eadn Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-bo-dao-nha-vs-uruguay-463-190010.html\">Uruguay 2-1 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: Ronaldo \u0111\u00f3ng phim m\u1ea5t t\u00edch, Seleccao cay \u0111\u1eafng r\u1eddi cu\u1ed9c ch\u01a1i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/oscar-tabarez-va-garra-charrua-bi-quyet-dua-uruguay-tro-lai-dinh-cao-389-189999.html\">\u00d3scar Tab\u00e1rez v\u00e0 Garra Charr\u00faa: B\u00ed quy\u1ebft \u0111\u01b0a Uruguay tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ec9nh cao</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"751","checkdouble":"190049"},{"date":"05:01 01/07","title":"\"NHM r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/nhm-rat-buon-khi-khong-co-messi-va-ronaldo-o-tu-ket.PNG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi, c\u1ef1u sao MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh NHM s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nHai c\u1eb7p \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018 \u0111\u00e3 di\u1ec5n ra. Argentina d\u00f9 r\u1ea5t c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 tr\u00e1nh kh\u1ecfi th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 3-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ph\u00e1p.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/nhm-rat-buon-khi-khong-co-messi-va-ronaldo-o-tu-ket.PNG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u sau \u0111\u00f3 kh\u00f4ng l\u00e2u Uruguay d\u00f9 c\u1ea7m b\u00f3ng v\u00e0 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m khi\u00eam t\u1ed1n h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u so v\u1edbi B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha nh\u01b0ng v\u1eabn gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng v\u1edbi t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 2-1. <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-bo-dao-nha-vs-uruguay-421-190013.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span> gi\u00fap \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 ti\u1ebfn v\u00e0o t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, h\u1ecd s\u1ebd \u0111\u1ee5ng \u0111\u1ed9 Ph\u00e1p.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNh\u01b0 v\u1eady l\u00e0 Argentina c\u1ee7a Messi v\u00e0 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha c\u1ee7a Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. C\u1ea3 M10 v\u00e0 CR7 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh h\u1ecd kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u00fap Argentina hay B\u0110N gi\u00e0nh nh\u1eefng chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Gary Neville ti\u1ebfc nu\u1ed1i khi Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo r\u1eddi gi\u1ea3i</h2>\r\n<h2>\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gary Neville ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi, c\u1ef1u sao MU kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh NHM s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t bu\u1ed3n khi kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ch\u1ee9ng ki\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo Messi\" title=\"Ronaldo Messi\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/17/mourinho-ve-ra-kich-ban-khong-tuong-cho-ronaldo-va-messi-o-world-cup-2018.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi c\u00f9ng d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cTh\u1eadt \u0111\u00e1ng ti\u1ebfc khi ch\u00fang ta kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c theo d\u00f5i Ronaldo v\u00e0 Messi ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c thi \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018, h\u1ecd l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao l\u1edbn v\u00e0 thu h\u00fat r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u NHM. T\u00f4i v\u00e0 r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V c\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y bu\u1ed3n khi M10 v\u00e0 CR7 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n\u201cRonaldo v\u00e0 Messi \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng \u1edf World Cup 2018, t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft l\u00e0 h\u1ecd c\u00f3 \u00fd \u0111\u1ecbnh chia tay \u0110TQG hay kh\u00f4ng, nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng t\u00f4i th\u1ea5y r\u1eb1ng h\u1ecd g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 n\u1eafm to\u00e0n b\u1ed9 tr\u1ecdng l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a \u0110TQG\u201d.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nV\u01b0\u01a1ng Ng\u00e2n (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"750","checkdouble":"190050"},{"date":"05:50 01/07","title":"D\u01b0 \u00e2m Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: Th\u00e0nh b\u1ea1i b\u1edfi nh\u1eefng h\u1ecdng s\u00fang","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/1/du-am-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-thanh-bai-boi-nhung-hong-sung.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018, phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. \r\n</h2><h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi c\u1ee7a Edison Cavani v\u00e0 Luis Suarez</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nB\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Edison Cavani v\u00e0 Luis Suarez \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018. Hai c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 n\u00e0y chi\u1ebfm 50% s\u1ee9c m\u1ea1nh c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9, v\u00e0 r\u1ed3i h\u1ecd \u0111\u00e3 kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ec3 NHM c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh ph\u1ea3i th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"\u0110i\u1ec3m nh\u1ea5n Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00f2ng 18 World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/Diem-nhan-Uruguay-vs-Bo-Dao-Nha-vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay ph\u00fat th\u1ee9 7 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f9ng nhau k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ea1o ra b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u1edf t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 cho Uruguay. C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng \u1edf khu v\u1ef1c gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n, anh chuy\u1ec1n b\u00f3ng cho ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Barca v\u00e0 b\u0103ng l\u00ean ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc.</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nT\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng di chuy\u1ec3n c\u1ef1c nhanh c\u1ee7a Cavani khi\u1ebfn b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i trung v\u1ec7 Fonte v\u00e0 Pepe c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ng\u1edd t\u1edbi, Suarez ch\u1ec9 ch\u1edd \u0111i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 tung m\u1ed9t \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng treo b\u00f3ng ch\u00ednh x\u00e1c t\u1edbi t\u1eebng x\u0103ng ti m\u00e9t.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCavani b\u0103ng v\u00e0o \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u tung l\u01b0\u1edbi Rui Patricio trong s\u1ef1 ng\u1ee1 ng\u00e0ng c\u1ee7a h\u00e0ng th\u1ee7 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 4 c\u1ee7a Cavani trong 3 k\u1ef3 World Cup g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t, \u0111\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng th\u1ee9 44 c\u1ee7a ng\u00f4i sao sinh n\u0103m 1987 trong m\u00e0u \u00e1o \u0110TQG.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-tran-uruguay-21-bo-dao-nha-421-190046.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha </span>ch\u1ec9 ra r\u1eb1ng 12/44 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Cavani cho Uruguay \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o b\u1edfi Luis Suarez, chi\u1ebfm 27%. \u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i n\u00e0y hi\u1ec3u nhau nh\u01b0 th\u1ebf n\u00e0o.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nK\u1ec3 t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1966, ch\u1ec9 Grzegorz Lato v\u00e0 Andrzej Szarmach (5, Ba Lan), Michael Ballack v\u00e0 Miroslav Klose (5, \u0110\u1ee9c) \u0111\u00e3 k\u1ebft h\u1ee3p t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u b\u00e0n th\u1eafng h\u01a1n b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Edinson Cavani v\u00e0 Luis Suarez (4, Uruguay).<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Cavani nang ty so len 2-1\" title=\"Cavani n\u00e2ng t\u1ef7 s\u1ed1 l\u00ean 2-1\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/cavabi.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Cavani t\u1ecfa s\u00e1ng v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00fap</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nT\u1edbi ph\u00fat 62, Cavani v\u00e0 Suarez ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c h\u1ee3p s\u1ee9c mang v\u1ec1 cho Uruguay b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u1ee9 2. T\u1eeb \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng ph\u00e1t b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Fernando Muslera, Rodrigo Bentancur c\u00f3 b\u00f3ng ngay tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nLuis Suarez nhanh ch\u00f3ng di chuy\u1ec3n v\u00e0o trung l\u1ed9 h\u00fat theo 3 c\u00e1i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o tr\u1eafng t\u1ea1o \u0111i\u1ec1u ki\u1ec7n cho Cavani \u1edf v\u00e0o t\u01b0 th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng b\u1ecb ai theo k\u00e8m,&nbsp;Bentancur m\u1edbm b\u00f3ng v\u1eeba t\u1ea7m \u0111\u1ec3 ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o kho\u00e1c \u00e1o PSG th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n c\u00fa c\u1ee9a l\u00f2ng ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n Rui Patricio, ghi b\u00e0n th\u1ee9 3 k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea7u&nbsp;gi\u1ea3i.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nC\u00f9ng v\u1edbi Ronaldo v\u00e0 Lukaku, Cavani ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t trong 3 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n c\u1ea3 b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u, ch\u00e2n tr\u00e1i v\u00e0 ch\u00e2n ph\u1ea3i \u1edf World Cup n\u00e0y.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nCavani ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ef1c t\u1ed1t, tr\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha anh c\u00f3 3 l\u1ea7n k\u1ebft th\u00fac, 2 tr\u00fang \u0111\u00edch v\u00e0 t\u1ea5t c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ec1u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c chuy\u1ec3n h\u00f3a th\u00e0nh&nbsp;b\u00e0n th\u1eafng. V\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh anh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00ecnh ch\u1ecdn l\u00e0 C\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc nh\u1ea5t tr\u1eadn.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSuarez kh\u00f4ng ghi b\u00e0n nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ec3 d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n trong vai tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o ho\u1eb7c di chuy\u1ec3n thu h\u00fat h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng, qua \u0111\u00f3 m\u1edf ra c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m cho c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u00e1 c\u1eb7p v\u1edbi m\u00ecnh tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<h2>Cristiano Ronaldo ch\u1ec9 \u0111em l\u1ea1i s\u1ef1 th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng</h2>\r\n<h2>&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ng\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1ea1i v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 nguy hi\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani, Ronaldo l\u1ea1i b\u1ea5t l\u1ef1c trong vi\u1ec7c t\u1ea1o ra kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t cho B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. M\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a CR7 \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Uruguay l\u00e0 r\u1ea5t m\u1edd nh\u1ea1t.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ronaldo dang gay that vong rat lon\" title=\"Ronaldo \u0111ang g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng r\u1ea5t l\u1edbn\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/5-diem-nhan-Uruguay-vs-Bo-Dao-Nha-vong-18-World-Cup-2018-hinh-anh.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Ronaldo ch\u01a1i th\u1ea5y v\u1ecdng \u1edf tr\u1eadn g\u1eb7p Uruguay</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nRonaldo b\u1ecb chia c\u1eaft ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u1edbi c\u00e1c v\u1ec7 tinh xung quanh, anh ch\u1ec9 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng n\u1ed7 l\u1ef1c \u0111\u1ed9t ph\u00e1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n ho\u1eb7c nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. Tuy nhi\u00ean, trong m\u1ed9t ng\u00e0y nh\u1eefng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 Uruguay ch\u01a1i ch\u1eb7t ch\u1ebd, CR7 \u0111\u00e3 b\u1ecb v\u00f4 hi\u1ec7u h\u00f3a ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTh\u1ed1ng k\u00ea cho th\u1ea5y, trong hi\u1ec7p \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean, Ronaldo ch\u1ea1m b\u00f3ng \u00edt kh\u00f3 tin v\u1edbi 24 l\u1ea7n, nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng l\u1ea7n n\u00e0o trong v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed1i ph\u01b0\u01a1ng.&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTrong 90 ph\u00fat thi \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc Uruguay, Cristiano Ronaldo \u0111\u00e3 d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m 6 l\u1ea7n, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n t\u1ed5ng s\u1ed1 l\u1ea7n d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 (5) nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nSi\u00eau sao \u0111ang kho\u00e1c \u00e1o Real Madrid v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng n\u00e0o \u1edf v\u00f2ng \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp World Cup, c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 33 tu\u1ed5i c\u00f3 6 l\u1ea7n ra s\u00e2n, tung ra 25 c\u00fa d\u1ee9t \u0111i\u1ec3m nh\u01b0ng kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u00f2ng 1/8 World Cup 2018, phong \u0111\u1ed9 tr\u00e1i ng\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ng\u00f4i sao tr\u00ean h\u00e0ng c\u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.&nbsp;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ro nen\" title=\"R\u00f4 n\u1ec1n\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/1/ro-8.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>Phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a nh\u1eefng ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ebfn k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nM\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a b\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani gi\u00fap Uruguay c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 2 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha trong ng\u00e0y Ronaldo g\u00e2y th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 1 pha l\u1eadp c\u00f4ng t\u1eeb c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Pepe.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\n<span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-bo-dao-nha-vs-uruguay-421-190013.html\" target=\"_blank\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span> gi\u00fap Suarez v\u00e0 Cavani ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c mang theo nh\u1eefng hy v\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a NHM trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Ph\u00e1p \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft, trong khi \u0111\u00f3 Ronaldo \u0111\u00e0nh ng\u1eadm ng\u00f9i c\u00f9ng Seleccao r\u1eddi Nga v\u1edbi th\u00e0nh t\u00edch l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng 1/8.</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><br>\r\nNguy\u1ec5n Huy\u1ec1n (TTVN)</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"749","checkdouble":"190052"},{"date":"06:58 01/07","title":"L\u1ecbch thi \u0111\u1ea5u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 h\u00f4m nay (1/7/2018)","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/original/2018/7/1/lich-thi-dau-bong-da-hom-nay-172018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:10