solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">01/07 19:00</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">Qu\u1ea3ng Ninh - H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i</td>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center; border: 1px solid rgb(221, 221, 221);\">VTV5</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n<br />\r\n<br /></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"748","checkdouble":"190055"},{"date":"13:13 30/06","title":"HLV Hierro ch\u1ed1t 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/hlv-hierro-chot-5-cau-thu-tay-ban-nha-da-luan-luu-11m.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n x\u1ee9 s\u1edf b\u00f2 t\u00f3t chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb s\u1eb5n s\u00e0ng cho kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng ph\u1ea3i d\u00f9ng lo\u1ea1t \u0111\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u may r\u1ee7i \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng thua v\u1edbi Nga \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8. </h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">Trong c\u00e1c bu\u1ed5i t\u1eadp g\u1ea7n \u0111\u00e2y, HLV Hierro cho c\u00e1c tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha\u00a0 t\u1eadp s\u00fat lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u r\u1ea5t k\u1ef9 tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i Moscow.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTheo t\u1edd AS, Hierro c\u0169ng \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ecdn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u0103m c\u00e1i t\u00ean s\u1ebd nh\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch trong lo\u1ea1t \"\u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang\" n\u1ebfu tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u b\u1ea5t ph\u00e2n th\u1eafng b\u1ea1i sau 120 ph\u00fat. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean cho T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd l\u00e0 David Silva. Ba ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u00fat sau anh s\u1ebd l\u00e0 Diego Costa, Isco v\u00e0 Sergio Busquets. Ng\u01b0\u1eddi s\u1ebd \u0111\u00e1 qu\u1ea3 quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh, n\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n, l\u00e0 Andres Iniesta.<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Hierro ch\u1ed1t 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Hierro ch\u1ed1t 5 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u 11m h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/tbn-3292-1530291497.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n T\u00e2y Ban Nha th\u1eadn tr\u1ecdng d\u00f9 g\u1eb7p Nga - \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u01b0a th\u00edch t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8. \u1ea2nh: AS.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nHLV Hierro c\u0169ng nghi\u00ean c\u1ee9u r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, n\u01a1i \u00f4ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng quy\u1ec1n thay ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u1ee9 t\u01b0 theo lu\u1eadt m\u1edbi m\u00e0 FIFA \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nD\u00f9 v\u1eady theo t\u1edd Marca (T\u00e2y Ban Nha), T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng h\u1ea1 Nga trong hai hi\u1ec7p ch\u00ednh, b\u1edfi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 gi\u00e0u th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c h\u01a1n \u201cLa Roja\u201d.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nL\u1ecbch s\u1eed ch\u1ee9ng minh Nga v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u01b0a th\u00edch c\u1ee7a T\u00e2y Ban Nha. \u0110\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 World Cup 2018 thua c\u1ea3 ba l\u1ea7n g\u1eb7p T\u00e2y Ban Nha t\u1ea1i c\u00e1c gi\u1ea3i l\u1edbn. \u1ede tr\u1eadn giao h\u1eefu g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o th\u00e1ng 11 n\u0103m ngo\u00e1i, hai \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00f2a 3-3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSergio Ramos ghi b\u00e0n t\u1eeb ch\u1ea5m ph\u1ea1t \u0111\u1ec1n trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u0111\u00f3, nh\u01b0ng th\u1ee7 qu\u00e2n T\u00e2y Ban Nha l\u1ea1i kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c Hierro tin t\u01b0\u1edfng giao tr\u1ecdng tr\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e1 lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i v\u00f2ng 1/8 t\u1edbi.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u gi\u1eefa Nga v\u00e0 T\u00e2y Ban Nha s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 21h ng\u00e0y 1/7, theo gi\u1edd H\u00e0 N\u1ed9i.</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"747","checkdouble":"189989"},{"date":"14:12 30/06","title":"Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Mbappe d\u00f9ng ti\u1ec1n th\u01b0\u1edfng t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018 \u0111\u1ec3 l\u00e0m t\u1eeb thi\u1ec7n","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/tien-dao-mbappe-dung-tien-thuong-tai-world-cup-2018-de-lam-tu-thien.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i nh\u1edd phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Real Madrid, nh\u01b0ng HLV Santos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nB\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c CR7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup, \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, th\u00ec 4 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo. Anh l\u1eadp hattrick trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n, ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 im ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady. thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Fernando Santos m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh vai tr\u00f2 v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, thay v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n CR7. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u0110T Uruguay, \u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft m\u1edbi gi\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Santos cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng, b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi Uruguay c\u00e2u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1ec1 Luis Suarez hay Edinson Cavani. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Santos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha\" title=\"BDN vs Iran Ronaldo di bong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/nhung-thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-sau-tran-dau-bdn-11-iran.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Santos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd thua. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi \u0110T Uruguay. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t HLV gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng su\u1ed1t 12 n\u0103m, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. C\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng v\u0169 kh\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c thua.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Santos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf t\u1eebng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, trong vi\u1ec7c h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Nam M\u1ef9. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 1h \u0111\u00eam nay (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam), d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin xung quanh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-1h00-ngay-17-trong-phao-doi-dau-462-189986.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-1h00-ngay-17-trong-phao-doi-dau.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-1h00-ngay-17-trong-phao-doi-dau-462-189986.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (1h00 ng\u00e0y 1/7): Tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai b\u00ean khai h\u1ecfa nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/suarez-nhan-ronaldo-toi-dang-tro-lai-day-nhe-421-189975.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/suarez-nhan-ronaldo-toi-dang-tro-lai-day-nhe.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/suarez-nhan-ronaldo-toi-dang-tro-lai-day-nhe-421-189975.html\">Suarez nh\u1eafn Ronaldo: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5y nh\u00e9!&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nLuis Suarez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Barcelona nh\u1eafn Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1eb1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/uruguay-khong-tap-trung-hoan-toan-vao-ronaldo-421-189843.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/uruguay-khong-tap-trung-hoan-toan-vao-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/uruguay-khong-tap-trung-hoan-toan-vao-ronaldo-421-189843.html\">Uruguay kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nSebastian Coates ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo, ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o CR7.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"746","checkdouble":"189990"},{"date":"15:10 30/06","title":"\"VAR \u0111ang ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u1edf World Cup 2018\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/var-dang-phat-huy-hieu-qua-o-world-cup-2018.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Li\u00ean \u0111o\u00e0n B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi (FIFA) kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR \u0111ang h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t cho tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111i\u1ec1u khi\u1ec3n tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup 2018.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">ESPN \u0111\u01b0a tin v\u1eeba qua, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch \u1ee6y ban Tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i FIFA Pierluigi Collina v\u00e0 c\u1ed9ng s\u1ef1 \u0111\u00e3 xem l\u1ea1i di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a 48 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018. K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3, c\u00f3 t\u1ed5ng c\u1ed9ng 335 t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c theo d\u00f5i k\u1ef9 l\u01b0\u1ee1ng b\u1edfi c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3, tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u00f4ng ngh\u00ea VAR h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 14 l\u1ea7n, t\u0103ng t\u1ef7 l\u1ec7 chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c trong c\u00e1c quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh t\u1eeb 95% l\u00ean 99,3%. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 tuy\u1ec7t \u0111\u1ed1i 100%. Tuy nhi\u00ean, 99,3% l\u00e0 con s\u1ed1 r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u00e0 ti\u1ec7m c\u1eadn v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 ho\u00e0n h\u1ea3o. C\u00e1c tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i \u0111ang nh\u1eadn h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 r\u1ea5t t\u1ed1t t\u1eeb VAR\u201d, Ch\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Collina l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng trong b\u1ed1i c\u1ea3nh VAR \u0111ang t\u1ea1o ra nhi\u1ec1u tranh c\u00e3i.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR \u0111ang ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR \u0111ang ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u1edf World Cup 2018 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/cthoyvartrialperiodcouldbedelayedbeyond2018worldcup20171005.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">FIFA kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh VAR \u0111ang h\u1ed7 tr\u1ee3 t\u1ed1t cho tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nTh\u1ed1ng k\u00ea m\u1edbi nh\u1ea5t t\u1eeb FIFA cho th\u1ea5y trung b\u00ecnh c\u00f3 4 pha ph\u1ea1m l\u1ed7i \u1edf m\u1ed7i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Th\u1ebb \u0111\u1ecf c\u0169ng gi\u1ea3m xu\u1ed1ng so v\u1edbi v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng c\u1ee7a c\u00e1c k\u1ef3 World Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 (3 th\u1ebb). D\u00f9 v\u1eady, l\u01b0\u1ee3ng penalty t\u0103ng \u0111\u1ed9t bi\u1ebfn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau 48 tr\u1eadn, c\u00f3 \u0111\u1ebfn 24 qu\u1ea3 penalty \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra. Con s\u1ed1 qu\u00e1 cao so v\u1edbi ch\u1ec9 10 penalty \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2010 v\u00e0 World cup 2014. 24 qu\u1ea3 penalty c\u0169ng l\u00e0 k\u1ef7 l\u1ee5c m\u1edbi c\u1ee7a World Cup, v\u01b0\u1ee3t xa so v\u1edbi con s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 18 qu\u1ea3 penalty.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nCh\u1ee7 t\u1ecbch Collina kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh VAR \u0111ang ph\u00e1t huy hi\u1ec7u qu\u1ea3 \u1edf ng\u00e0y h\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 l\u1edbn nh\u1ea5t h\u00e0nh tinh v\u00e0 FIFA s\u1ebd s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng l\u00e2u d\u00e0i c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 n\u00e0y. \u201cCh\u00fang t\u00f4i ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 s\u1eed d\u1ee5ng VAR \u1edf nhi\u1ec1u gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u trong t\u01b0\u01a1ng lai. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi ch\u1ea1y, b\u1ea1n ph\u1ea3i \u0111i b\u1ed9, c\u0169ng gi\u1ed1ng nh\u01b0 vi\u1ec7c th\u1eed nghi\u1ec7m c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR v\u1eady\u201d, \u00f4ng nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nFIFA cho r\u1eb1ng VAR kh\u00f4ng g\u00e2y \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1ed1c \u0111\u1ed9 v\u00e0 ch\u1ea5t l\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea ch\u1ec9 r\u00f5 th\u1eddi gian b\u00f9 gi\u1edd trung b\u00ecnh \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup 2018 ch\u1ec9 t\u0103ng th\u00eam m\u1ed9t ph\u00fat (t\u1eeb 5 ph\u00fat l\u00ean 6 ph\u00fat).<br>\r\n<h2>C\u00e1c b\u00e0i kh\u00e1c v\u1ec1 c\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR\u00a0t\u1ea1i\u00a0World Cup 2018\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/vi-sao-trong-tai-cakir-khong-thoi-11m-cho-nigeria-du-ap-dung-var-421-189703.html\">V\u00ec sao tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i Cakir kh\u00f4ng th\u1ed5i 11m cho Nigeria d\u00f9 \u00e1p d\u1ee5ng VAR?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-nuoc-anh-chui-boi-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-bo-dao-nha-421-189575.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i n\u01b0\u1edbc Anh ch\u1eedi b\u1edbi VAR sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/christian-eriksen-tuyen-bo-ghet-var-sau-tran-hoa-cua-dan-mach-465-189199.html\">Christian Eriksen tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 gh\u00e9t VAR sau tr\u1eadn h\u00f2a c\u1ee7a \u0110an M\u1ea1ch</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/cong-nghe-var-bat-viet-vi-ra-sao-461-189194.html\">C\u00f4ng ngh\u1ec7 VAR b\u1eaft vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb ra sao</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/goc-nhin-world-cup-2018/var-tai-world-cup-2018-lan-ranh-giua-duoc-va-mat-466-189193.html\">VAR t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: L\u1eb1n ranh gi\u1eefa \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u00e0 m\u1ea5t</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/nghi-an-trong-tai-mat-lien-lac-var-tran-bdn-10-morocco-421-189125.html\">Nghi \u00e1n tr\u1ecdng t\u00e0i m\u1ea5t li\u00ean l\u1ea1c VAR tr\u1eadn B\u0110N 1-0 Morocco</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/amrabat-phat-bieu-ve-cong-nghe-var-421-189101.html\">Sao Ma R\u1ed1c g\u00e2y s\u1ed1c: \u201cVAR l\u00e0 th\u1ee9 v\u00f4 d\u1ee5ng\u201d</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"745","checkdouble":"189992"},{"date":"15:17 30/06","title":"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ozil n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/tien-ve-ozil-noi-gi-ve-ky-world-cup-2018-tham-hoa.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Tr\u1edf v\u1ec1 n\u01b0\u1edbc sau th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i cay \u0111\u1eafng c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n \u0110\u1ee9c tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, l\u1ea7n \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean Mesut Ozil ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c l\u00ean ti\u1ebfng.</h2><div style=\"text-align: left;\">K\u1ec3 t\u1eeb khi nh\u00e0 v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2014 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \"c\u1ef1u v\u01b0\u01a1ng\" ngay sau v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng, h\u00e0ng lo\u1ea1t l\u1eddi ch\u1ec9 tr\u00edch \u0111\u1ed5 d\u1ed3n l\u00ean \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 s\u1ed1 10 Mesut Oezil.\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ozil n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Ozil n\u00f3i g\u00ec v\u1ec1 k\u1ef3 World Cup 2018 th\u1ea3m h\u1ecda h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/30/po.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">Oezil t\u00e2m s\u1ef1 tr\u00ean m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\nNgay tr\u01b0\u1edbc th\u1ec1m gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u, ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Arsenal \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ec1 t\u00e0i g\u00e2y tranh c\u00e3i khi c\u00f3 b\u1ee9c h\u00ecnh ch\u1ee5p chung v\u1edbi T\u1ed5ng th\u1ed1ng Th\u1ed5 Nh\u0129 K\u1ef3 Recep Tayyip Erdogan. Ti\u1ebfp theo \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n \u0111\u00e1ng th\u1ea5t v\u1ecdng trong tr\u1eadn ra qu\u00e2n, khi\u1ebfn \u0110\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3i ch\u1ecbu th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 0-1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Mexico.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y l\u00ean b\u0103ng gh\u1ebf d\u1ef1 b\u1ecb \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Oezil l\u1ea1i ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c c\u00f3 t\u00ean trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh ch\u00ednh th\u1ee9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c. Nh\u01b0ng c\u1ea3 2 l\u1ea7n anh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ra s\u00e2n, \"Die Mannschaft\" \u0111\u1ec1u b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn, qua \u0111\u00f3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh nh\u00e0 \u0110KV\u0110 th\u1ee9 3 li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp b\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nPh\u1ea3i \u0111\u00f3n nh\u1eadn c\u01a1n m\u01b0a \"g\u1ea1ch \u0111\u00e1\" t\u1eeb truy\u1ec1n th\u00f4ng v\u00e0 m\u1ea1ng x\u00e3 h\u1ed9i, s\u1ed1 10 cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng c\u0169ng quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 s\u1ef1 im l\u1eb7ng. Tr\u00ean trang Instagram c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, Oezil chia s\u1ebb: \"Th\u1eadt \u0111au \u0111\u1edbn khi ph\u1ea3i r\u1eddi kh\u1ecfi World Cup ngay t\u1eeb v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e3 thi \u0111\u1ea5u kh\u00f4ng \u0111\u1ee7 t\u1ed1t. T\u00f4i s\u1ebd c\u1ea7n th\u00eam th\u1eddi gian \u0111\u1ec3 v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua c\u00fa s\u1ed1c n\u00e0y\" k\u00e8m theo hashtah #SayNoToRacism (N\u00f3i kh\u00f4ng v\u1edbi ph\u00e2n bi\u1ec7t ch\u1ee7ng t\u1ed9c).<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau tr\u1eadn thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc H\u00e0n Qu\u1ed1c, m\u1ed9t C\u0110V qu\u00e1 kh\u00edch \u0111\u00e3 t\u00ecm c\u00e1ch g\u00e2y h\u1ea5n v\u1edbi Oezil. R\u1ea5t may khi l\u1ef1c l\u01b0\u1ee3ng an ninh \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t k\u1ecbp th\u1eddi tr\u01b0\u1edbc khi 2 b\u00ean x\u1ea3y ra \u1ea9u \u0111\u1ea3 l\u1edbn.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"744","checkdouble":"189993"},{"date":"15:49 30/06","title":"HLV B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha: \"N\u1ebfu d\u1ef1a d\u1eabm v\u00e0o Ronaldo, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i thua ch\u1eafc\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/hlv-bo-dao-nha-neu-dua-dam-vao-ronaldo-chung-toi-thua-chac.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>D\u00f9 v\u1eabn \u0111ang b\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111i nh\u1edd phong \u0111\u1ed9 c\u1ee7a si\u00eau sao Real Madrid, nh\u01b0ng HLV Santos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t th\u00e1i \u0111\u1ed9 r\u1ea5t b\u00ecnh th\u1ea3n.\r\n</h2><h2><br>\r\nB\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c CR7<br>\r\n&nbsp;</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u1ede giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng World Cup, \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 5 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, th\u00ec 4 trong s\u1ed1 \u0111\u00f3 thu\u1ed9c v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo. Anh l\u1eadp hattrick trong tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1edf m\u00e0n, ghi b\u00e0n duy nh\u1ea5t tr\u01b0\u1edbc Ma R\u1ed1c, v\u00e0 ch\u1ec9 im ti\u1ebfng tr\u01b0\u1edbc Iran trong l\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1eadn cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 v\u1eady. thuy\u1ec1n tr\u01b0\u1edfng Fernando Santos m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa nh\u1ea5n m\u1ea1nh vai tr\u00f2 v\u00e0 t\u1ea7m quan tr\u1ecdng c\u1ee7a t\u1eadp th\u1ec3, thay v\u00ec ch\u1ec9 n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n CR7. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u lo\u1ea1i tr\u1ef1c ti\u1ebfp v\u1edbi \u0110T Uruguay, \u00f4ng hi\u1ec3u r\u1eb1ng ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 s\u1ef1 \u0111o\u00e0n k\u1ebft m\u1edbi gi\u00fap B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha v\u01b0\u1ee3t qua \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Santos cho bi\u1ebft: &ldquo;M\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u1ec1u bi\u1ebft r\u1eb1ng, b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i ph\u1ee5 thu\u1ed9c v\u00e0o c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u1ea5t nhi\u00ean, ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1edf h\u1eefu c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc b\u1eadc nh\u1ea5t v\u00e0o th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y, nh\u01b0ng b\u1ea1n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 h\u1ecfi Uruguay c\u00e2u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 v\u1ec1 Luis Suarez hay Edinson Cavani. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng n\u00e0o c\u0169ng s\u1edf h\u1eefu nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1eb3ng c\u1ea5p.&rdquo;<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Santos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha\" title=\"BDN vs Iran Ronaldo di bong\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/6/26/nhung-thong-ke-khong-the-bo-qua-sau-tran-dau-bdn-11-iran.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\r\n            <h3>HLV Santos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0110T B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n&ldquo;Nh\u01b0ng t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 l\u00e0 quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u1ea5t. N\u1ebfu ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u1ec3 Ronaldo thi \u0111\u1ea5u m\u1ed9t m\u00ecnh, B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha s\u1ebd thua. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ph\u1ea3i chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u nh\u01b0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng, \u0111i\u1ec1u t\u01b0\u01a1ng t\u1ef1 c\u0169ng di\u1ec5n ra v\u1edbi \u0110T Uruguay. H\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 m\u1ea1nh m\u1ebd, s\u1edf h\u1eefu m\u1ed9t HLV gi\u00e0u kinh nghi\u1ec7m \u0111\u00e3 g\u1eafn b\u00f3 v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng su\u1ed1t 12 n\u0103m, m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 h\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea7u.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">&ldquo;T\u00f4i ngh\u0129 r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e2y s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi. C\u1ea3 2 \u0111\u1ed9i s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, t\u1eadn d\u1ee5ng v\u0169 kh\u00ed c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh. T\u00f4i hy v\u1ecdng v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0111\u1ec9nh cao. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n kh\u00e1c bi\u1ec7t v\u1edbi giai \u0111o\u1ea1n v\u00f2ng b\u1ea3ng. Kh\u00f4ng quan tr\u1ecdng \u0111i\u1ec3m s\u1ed1, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 th\u1eafng ho\u1eb7c thua.&rdquo;<br>\r\n&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">V\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec HLV Santos chia s\u1ebb v\u1ec1 Ronaldo, c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 th\u1ea5y B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111ang r\u1ea5t quy\u1ebft t\u00e2m \u1edf t\u1eebng c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n, trong vi\u1ec7c h\u1ea1 g\u1ee5c \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb Nam M\u1ef9. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o l\u00fac 1h \u0111\u00eam nay (gi\u1edd Vi\u1ec7t Nam), d\u01b0\u1edbi \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 nh\u1eefng th\u00f4ng tin xung quanh tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-1h00-ngay-17-trong-phao-doi-dau-462-189986.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-1h00-ngay-17-trong-phao-doi-dau.png\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-uruguay-vs-bo-dao-nha-1h00-ngay-17-trong-phao-doi-dau-462-189986.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha (1h00 ng\u00e0y 1/7): Tr\u1ecdng ph\u00e1o \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u</span><br>\r\nTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea1i chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c k\u1ef3 v\u1ecdng s\u1ebd l\u00e0 ng\u00e0y c\u00e1c ch\u00e2n s\u00fat th\u01b0\u1ee3ng th\u1eb7ng c\u1ee7a c\u1ea3 hai b\u00ean khai h\u1ecfa nh\u01b0ng th\u1eadt kh\u00f3 \u0111\u1ec3 tr\u00f4ng ch\u1edd v\u00e0o m\u1ed9t th\u1ebf...</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/suarez-nhan-ronaldo-toi-dang-tro-lai-day-nhe-421-189975.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/30/suarez-nhan-ronaldo-toi-dang-tro-lai-day-nhe.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/suarez-nhan-ronaldo-toi-dang-tro-lai-day-nhe-421-189975.html\">Suarez nh\u1eafn Ronaldo: &ldquo;T\u00f4i \u0111ang tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ea5y nh\u00e9!&rdquo;</span><br>\r\nLuis Suarez ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn Uruguay vs B\u1ed3 \u0110\u00e0o Nha. Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a Barcelona nh\u1eafn Cristiano Ronaldo v\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i r\u1eb1ng phong \u0111\u1ed9 cao nh\u1ea5t c\u1ee7a anh v\u1eabn ch\u01b0a t\u1edbi.</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/uruguay-khong-tap-trung-hoan-toan-vao-ronaldo-421-189843.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/6/28/uruguay-khong-tap-trung-hoan-toan-vao-ronaldo.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/uruguay-khong-tap-trung-hoan-toan-vao-ronaldo-421-189843.html\">Uruguay kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o Ronaldo</span><br>\r\nSebastian Coates ph\u00e1t bi\u1ec3u v\u1ec1 Cristiano Ronaldo, ng\u00f4i sao 28 tu\u1ed5i kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng Nam M\u1ef9 s\u1ebd kh\u00f4ng t\u1eadp trung ho\u00e0n to\u00e0n v\u00e0o CR7.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nguy\u1ec7t Anh (TTVN)</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"743","checkdouble":"189994"}]}